eWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":14}],"windowDisplayName":"카논","body":"……저. ……말을 잘 못 해서……\n2, 2학년입니다, 고등학교……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":14,"motionName":"sad01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":14,"voiceId":"episode053-005","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":14}],"windowDisplayName":"카논","body":"또…… 무슨 얘기를 해야……\n응? 미사키 짱, 뭐라고?\n……평소 하는 일……?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":14,"motionName":"odoodo02","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":14,"voiceId":"episode053-006","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":14}],"windowDisplayName":"카논","body":"부활동은 다도부입니다……\n아직 공부할 게 많아서 어렵지만\n즐거워요.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":14,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":14,"voiceId":"episode053-007","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":14}],"windowDisplayName":"카논","body":"드럼도 원래 잘 못해서 그만두려고 했어요.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":14,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":14,"voiceId":"episode053-008","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":14}],"windowDisp